<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604467794349-0b74285de7e7?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8MjN8fGJhYnklMjBjbG90aGVzfGVufDB8fDB8&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=60);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Green Cub wear, <strong>a baby wardrobe for every step of the way</strong>!</h1>
    <p>Your desired baby clothing, one click away.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-flat" href="#">Search</a>
  </div>
